<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para><db:link xlink:href="qt3drender-qscreenraycaster.xml">QScreenRayCaster</db:link> can be used to perform ray casting tests by specifying coordinates in screen space, which will be used to construct an actual 3D ray between the near and far planes.</db:para>
